# Copy this file to ".env" (same folder) and fill in your real values.
# Required for Exercises 1, 2, 4 (Stage 2 only), and 5. Exercise 3 needs no
# Azure setup at all — it's a deterministic risk-flagging + human-input demo.
# See README.md for the full step-by-step Azure OpenAI walkthrough.
#
# NOTE: the example deployment name below is a placeholder — Azure's available
# models have been changing rapidly through 2026. Check Azure AI Foundry's
# deployment screen for what's actually deployable in your region. Every
# script in this module uses the standard chat completions + tool-calling
# API, which works the same regardless of whether you end up with a
# reasoning or non-reasoning model — automatic temperature fallback is
# built in throughout.
#
# NEVER commit the real .env file to source control.

AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource-name.openai.azure.com/
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=agentic-ai-deploy
AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION=2024-10-21
